[L. Tom Perry Special Collections]], [[Harold B. Lee Library]], [[Brigham Young University]]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = [[List of awards and nominations received by James Stewart|Awards for James Stewart]]\n|list =\n{{AcademyAwardBestActor 1927-1940}}\n{{Academy Honorary Award}}\n{{AFI Life Achievement Award}}\n{{Cecil B. DeMille Award 1952\u20131975}}\n{{Distinguished Performance Award}}\n{{Lincoln Center Gala Tribute}}\n{{GoldenGlobeBestActorTVDrama 1969-1989}}\n{{Hasty Pudding Man of the Year}}\n{{Honorary Golden Bear}}\n{{Kennedy Center Honorees 1980s}}\n{{National Football Foundation Distinguished American Award}}\n{{New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Actor}}\n{{ScreenActorsGuildAward LifeAchievement 1960\u20131979}}\n{{Silver Bear for Best Actor}}\n{{Volpi Cup for Best Actor}}\n}}\n{{Indiana, Pennsylvania}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stewart, James}}\n[[Category:1908 births]]\n[[Category:1997 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:20th-century American poets]]\n[[Category:20th-century Presbyterians]]\n[[Category:Academy Honorary Award recipients]]\n[[Category:AFI Life Achievement Award recipients]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male poets]]\n[[Category:American male radio actors]]\n[[Category:American male stage actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:American male voice actors]]\n[[Category:American air force personnel of the Vietnam War]]\n[[Category:American people of Scottish descent]]\n[[Category:American Presbyterians]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Best Actor Academy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Best Drama Actor Golden Globe (television) winners]]\n[[Category:Broadway theatre people]]\n[[Category:Burials at Forest Lawn Memorial Park (Glendale)]]\n[[Category:California Republicans]]\n[[Category:Cecil B. DeMille Award Golden Globe winners]]\n[[Category:Commercial aviators]]\n[[Category:Deaths from pulmonary embolism]]\n[[